<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Our Website</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .links a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .description {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%-include("./navbar.ejs") %>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>
      <div class="description">
        <p>
          Our website offers a secure and user-friendly experience for managing
          your account. We employ advanced technologies such as bcrypt for
          secure password hashing and JWT (JSON Web Tokens) for safe and
          efficient authentication.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you sign up, your password is securely hashed using bcrypt,
          ensuring that even in the unlikely event of a data breach, your
          password remains protected. During login, JWT tokens are used to
          maintain a secure session, providing you with a seamless and secure
          browsing experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%-include("./footer.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
